sentences: Jai Waetford (born 25 January 1999) is an Australian pop singer and songwriter who came third on the fifth season of The X Factor Australia.
Waetford's self-titled debut EP was released in December 2013 and peaked at number 21 on the ARIA Albums Chart.
Waetford joined the Australian soap opera Neighbours in February 2016 as Angus Beaumont-Hannay; his debut episode aired on 2 May.
